@startuml
title Arena Master — Vista de Despliegue
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

node "PC Usuario\n(Navegador)" as Client {
  artifact "SPA Angular\nhttp://localhost:4200" as SPA
}

node "Servidor de Aplicación" as AppServer {
  artifact "Spring Boot API\nhttp://localhost:8080" as API
}

database "DB\n(PostgreSQL/MySQL)\n:5432/:3306" as DB

SPA --> API : REST/JSON\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT
API --> DB : JPA/Hibernate\nSQL

note right of SPA
Dev:
Angular usa proxy.conf.json:
/api -> http://localhost:8080
end note

note right of API
Spring Security:
- /api/auth/** público
- GET /api/** autenticado
- POST/PUT/DELETE según ROLE_ADMIN
end note
@enduml
